edge: Jared Leto portrays the character of Dr. Michael Morbius in the movie.
Charlie Shotwell portrays a young version of Michael's surrogate brother.

Matt Smith plays the role of Lucien, who is later called Milo by Michael due to sharing a bed with many previous boys named Milo. This character suffers from the same rare blood disease as Michael and gains similar abilities.
Lucien / Milo Morbius is Michael's surrogate brother.
